>>>> this whole effort. We need to continue Secretary Kerry=E2=80=99s effor=
ts to move
>>>> toward a diplomatic solution to the civil war in Syria that paves the =
way
>>>> for new leadership and enables Syrians from every community to take on
>>>> ISIS. Investing the Russians in this outcome and getting them to step =
up
>>>> and do their part will be difficult but essential. And we have to purs=
ue a
